## 📊 Analysis Output

```text
[+] Identifying project ecosystem...
[+] Enumerating software components...
[+] Mapping vulnerability intelligence...
[+] Evaluating reachability heuristics...

Detected Ecosystems: Python, Node.js

=== Reachable Vulnerabilities ===
✔ PyYAML (CRITICAL / CVE-2023-4567)
✔ lodash (HIGH / CVE-2023-9999)

=== Lower-Confidence / Noise Findings ===
✘ requests (HIGH / CVE-2022-1234)

=== Security Metrics ===
Total Vulnerabilities      : 3
Potential Noise Findings   : 1
Reachability Improvement : 33.3%
```

---

## 🏗️ Architecture
- **Ecosystem Detector**: Fingerprints projects based on marker files.
- **Reachability Engine**: Language-agnostic heuristic analysis (regex & string pattern).
- **Reporting Layer**: Professional, high-signal CLI experience via Rich.

